spec_data.Name: perl-SOAP-WSDL
spec_data.Description:
SOAP::WSDL provides easy access to Web Services with WSDL descriptions.
The WSDL is parsed and stored in memory. Your data is serialized according
to the rules in the WSDL. The only transport mechanisms currently supported
are HTTP and HTTPS.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 03:36:55 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Perl module for SOAP with WSDL support
